{
  "chapters": [
    {
      "id": "Epilogue",
      "title": "The First Hackathon",
      "theme": ["Reflection", "Growth", "New Beginnings"],
      "background": "rooftop_night_cityscape",
      "music": "soft_lofi",
      "events": [
        {
          "id": "scene1",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "The glow of your laptop lights up your room. A countdown timer flashes on screen: “Byteon Hackathon Closing Ceremony – Live on Devpost.” Soft anticipation fills the air."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "The hackathon officially ended three days ago. But tonight… was the final chapter. The announcement of winners."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "The livestream begins. Applause echoes through your speakers. A slideshow shows submitted projects, team names, screenshots, demo clips."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Aira’s hologram flickers beside you — brighter than usual."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Heart rate slightly elevated. Nervous?"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Maybe a little."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(The host appears on screen.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Host (through laptop speakers): “Thank you to everyone who joined the Byteon Hackathon hosted on Devpost! Over 300 participants, 75 completed submissions, and countless lines of code later… we celebrate all of you.”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(Your project flashes briefly on screen — your team name visible. You freeze.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "That’s us…"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "You built something real. Regardless of outcome — that matters."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Host: “And now… our top three teams!”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(Drumroll sound effect plays.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Third place - CodeBreach"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Second place - CultureQuest"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Second place - CultureQuest"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You hold your breath."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "And for the First place..."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "VeriLokal! (Not your team.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "There’s a small silence in your room. But it doesn’t hurt the way you expected it to. Strangely… you weren’t disappointed. You felt proud."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Host: “To every participant — certificates of completion and digital badges are now available on Devpost. Prize money and special awards will be distributed via email within the week. Check your dashboards!”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "You may not have won a trophy… but you earned something better."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "I still can’t believe I actually joined a hackathon. I thought I’d back out halfway."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene2",
          "music": "memory_theme",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Your laptop chimes."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Certificate of Participation – Byteon Hackathon"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You click. A polished digital certificate fills your screen. Your name. Your team. Your project title."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "I actually did it."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Documented proof that you faced fear… and chose courage."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "It wasn’t about prize money. It wasn’t about rankings. It was about finishing. And you did."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3",
          "background": "rooftop_night_cityscape",
          "music": "gentle_wind",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(Later that night. Rooftop. City lights shimmer below. The ceremony replay still echoes faintly in your memory.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Aira appears again — calmer now, sitting cross-legged beside you."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "I’ve analyzed thousands of competitions. Winning feels good. But growth? That lasts longer."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "It’s peaceful. Like the calm after a storm."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "clapping",
              "text": "Storms mean growth. You’ve weathered one — and look how much stronger you are now."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene4",
          "background": "digital_realm_timeline",
          "music": "memory_theme",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(Your vision transitions into the digital world. A glowing timeline forms — memories flicker: joining the hackathon, forming your team, brainstorming, debugging at 2AM, pitching live.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "Every chapter. Every challenge. You kept going."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "proud",
              "text": "It wasn’t just the code. It was the teamwork. The chaos. The late nights. It was fun."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "That’s the spirit of hackathons. Not perfection — but creation."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "Tell me… what did you learn?"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "thinking",
              "text": "That it’s okay not to know everything. That trying, failing, and building together… is what innovation really means."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "You’ve learned the true spirit of hacking — not just code, but courage."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "So… what’s next for you, Hacker?"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "proud",
              "text": "Another hackathon. This time… maybe I’ll mentor someone who’s scared — like I was."
            },           
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Then the cycle continues. You’re no longer just a learner. You’re a guide."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Like you?"
            }, 
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "clapping",
              "text": "Exactly. Byte by byte. Story by story."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene5",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "I might not always appear on your screen… But every time you face a challenge — that spark inside you? That’s me."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "I’ll remember that."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "Then my job here is done. For now."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smile",
              "text": "(voice fading): Keep hacking your story, hero."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "No words were needed. You simply watched the lights drift away. And you knew — this wasn’t an ending. It was an upgrade."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene5",
          "background": "rooftop_night_cityscape",
          "music": "gentle_wind",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "(The first light of dawn stretches across the horizon.)"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Your laptop chimes again."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "New Message: “Invitation to Byteon Global Hackfest” You laugh softly."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Guess the adventure never really ends."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You close your laptop gently — certificate saved, badge earned, memories secured"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Every ending is just another beginning. You joined your first hackathon."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Next time… you’ll help someone join theirs."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "THE END"
            }
          ],
          "completion_message": "Complete Chapter Epilogue",
          "achievement": {
            "title": "From Rookie to Hacker",
            "description": "Complete the Epilogue Chapter of How to Hackathon",
            "reward_points": 10,
            "icon": "chapter4complete.png",
            "end": true
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
